description.content:
Hi There!


Looking for a professional Squarespace expert to design & develop your Squarespace website or Squarespace eCommerce store?


A Professional freelance designer with a passion for web design (Front-end).Depending on your requirements, I will create a high-quality, beautiful Squarespace website or Squarespace online store that will beat your competitors.


WE ARE OFFERINGS:


  • New Squarespace website.
  • Redesign Squarespace site for more visitor attraction 
  • Squarespace website development
  • eCommerce and none eCommerce 
  • Squarespace online store setup and product upload 
  • Squarespace landing page design
  • Member area and Booking Features. 
  • Fix Squarespace error
  • Add Custom Code (Where needed)


We can help you build the following categories:


  • Business or Portfolio
  • Health & Fitness 
  • Motivational Speaker
  • Landing Page
  • Personal Blog & Magazine
  • Design From Sketch
  • Travel
  • Other CMS to Squarespace


WHY CHOOSE ME?


  • Unlimited Revision. 
  • 30 Days Free Support. (After Complete order)
  • No Compromise On Quality
  • A complete guide on how to edit and maintain Squarespace website easily without hiring a developer
  • Connecting custom domain


Connect with me today for FREE Consultation for your Squarespace site

questionsAndAnswers.question: What kind of websites do you offer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Entertainment, Non-profit, Real estate, Wedding, Portfolio, Services, Music, Legal, salon, Gym, Health & Fitness, Blog & Magazine, Corporate, Education, LAW, Firm, Freelancing, Construction, Creative, Technology, eCommerce Stores, etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What services do you offer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We are offering a complete Squarespace website design and redesign Squarespace website. Also, We are offering Customization on your existing Squarespace website. Additionally, we can fix any errors, and optimize your Squarespace website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is it possible to build the website according to my reference site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, Definitely I can create exactly as per your requirements. You will receive a far better product than your example site. If you want a 100% similar website, your reference site should be in  Squarespace.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many revisions do you provide?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I offer unlimited revisions until you are satisfied with my work.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you build Adult or porn website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I apologize. I'm not familiar with that kind of stuff.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What information is required for my project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Your Squarespace account login + Password. Your Project details and requirements. Any reference website link if you have : )

questionsAndAnswers.question: Does your gig price include Hosting & Domain too?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, you will have to provide me with Hosting & Domain.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can I get in touch with you? So can we communicate easily?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Unfortunately no, this is totally against Fiverr TOS! All communication with the client is to be done in writing via the Fiverr message board.

Highly recommend him for any web tasks, especially Squarespace forms!
